[MIYUKI] The mechanics of
your game are a little unclear.

00:16:29.614 --> 00:16:31.449 position:50% align:center
But I say we give
this thing a shot!

00:16:31.533 --> 00:16:32.575 position:50% align:center
I second that!

00:16:32.659 --> 00:16:35.161 position:50% align:center
Brave boys are best boys!

00:16:35.245 --> 00:16:36.913 position:50% align:center
I'll get it set up!

00:16:38.415 --> 00:16:41.042 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI, YU gasp]
She meant a balloon?!

00:16:41.126 --> 00:16:43.420 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR] A game where you pump
it as many times as you want,

00:16:43.503 --> 00:16:45.880 position:50% align:center
but you have to pump it
at least once to be relieved

00:16:45.964 --> 00:16:48.008 position:50% align:center
and if you reach
the limit you lose!

