You can pump it as many times
as your heart desires, but

00:16:54.597 --> 00:16:56.016 position:50% align:center
in order for your turn to end,

00:16:56.099 --> 00:16:57.851 position:50% align:center
you have to pump
it at least once.

00:16:57.934 --> 00:17:00.645 position:50% align:center
You go until the balloon
reaches its limit and bursts!

00:17:00.729 --> 00:17:01.980 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
I see.

00:17:02.063 --> 00:17:04.774 position:50% align:center
Guess I'm the only one
with my mind in the gutter?

00:17:04.858 --> 00:17:07.485 position:50% align:center
Where'd all that enthusiasm
you had run off to?

00:17:07.569 --> 00:17:09.863 position:50% align:center
They'll catch on if we
refuse to participate now.

00:17:09.946 --> 00:17:11.614 position:50% align:center
When you're right, you're right.

00:17:11.698 --> 00:17:14.034 position:50% align:center
I feel like she
set us up on purpose.

00:17:14.117 --> 00:17:15.869 position:50% align:center
I'm not so sure about that.

00:17:15.952 --> 00:17:18.329 position:50% align:center
She's one puzzle
I can never seem to solve.

00:17:18.413 --> 00:17:20.040 position:50% align:center
Where did you get this?

00:17:20.123 --> 00:17:23.084 position:50% align:center
Remember all those balloons we
let fly at the sports festival?

00:17:23.168 --> 00:17:26.254 position:50% align:center
I didn't wanna throw away the
leftovers, so I kept a big one!

00:17:26.338 --> 00:17:28.340 position:50% align:center
What an ecological thing to do!

00:17:28.423 --> 00:17:30.967 position:50% align:center
You ladies are gonna join in
on the fun, too, aren't you?

00:17:31.051 --> 00:17:33.219 position:50% align:center
Oh, uh, sure. Count me in.

00:17:33.303 --> 00:17:35.930 position:50% align:center
If everyone else is playing it,
then might as well.

00:17:36.014 --> 00:17:38.016 position:50% align:center
In that case, we'll have
the president go first,

00:17:38.099 --> 00:17:41.478 position:50% align:center
followed by Kaguya, then
Ishigami, then me, then Miko!

00:17:41.561 --> 00:17:43.313 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR] Let the pumping
commence.

00:17:43.396 --> 00:17:44.856 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
At least there's no "punishment"

00:17:44.939 --> 00:17:46.524 position:50% align:center
if I wind up failing.

00:17:46.608 --> 00:17:51.071 position:50% align:center
Unless I count the balloon
popping in my face, that is.

00:17:51.154 --> 00:17:54.157 position:50% align:center
But it's all in good fun.
Doesn't bother me a bit.

00:17:54.240 --> 00:17:55.950 position:50% align:center
Been a while since I played a
low-stress game.

00:17:56.034 --> 00:17:58.036 position:50% align:center
[YU grunting]

00:17:58.119 --> 00:18:03.124 position:50% align:center
[grunting]

00:18:06.961 --> 00:18:08.463 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI] You're, uh,
really blowin' it up!

00:18:08.546 --> 00:18:09.756 position:50% align:center
[CHIKA] Yes!

