[MIYUKI]
No, this is bad!

00:18:11.925 --> 00:18:15.428 position:50% align:center
I'll freak out if that thing
pops right in front of me!

00:18:15.512 --> 00:18:17.180 position:50% align:center
And if Shinomiya sees--

00:18:17.263 --> 00:18:18.973 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
Scared by a balloon popping?

00:18:19.057 --> 00:18:21.810 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA giggles]
You really are quite cute.

00:18:21.893 --> 00:18:25.188 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI groans]
Get a grip! Look!

00:18:25.271 --> 00:18:27.649 position:50% align:center
Shinomiya's not
fazed in the slightest!

00:18:27.732 --> 00:18:30.527 position:50% align:center
How can I call myself a man?!

00:18:30.610 --> 00:18:32.696 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR] Partaking
in balloon popping games

00:18:32.779 --> 00:18:37.117 position:50% align:center
is as foreign to Kaguya as
putting sushi on a cheeseburger.

00:18:37.200 --> 00:18:39.494 position:50% align:center
So, naturally, she's nervous.

00:18:39.577 --> 00:18:41.871 position:50% align:center
She's bright,
but she's a teenager.

00:18:41.955 --> 00:18:46.418 position:50% align:center
And like any teenager, she has
a distinct fear of the unknown.

00:18:47.752 --> 00:18:50.547 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR]
Oh! Uh! Never mind!

00:18:50.630 --> 00:18:52.257 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA scoffs]
Honestly,

00:18:52.340 --> 00:18:55.927 position:50% align:center
what's so scary about
putting air in a balloon?

00:18:56.011 --> 00:18:57.387 position:50% align:center
[CHIKA]
You're doing it wrong.

00:18:57.470 --> 00:18:59.973 position:50% align:center
You gotta use both hands
to pump it for maximum power!

00:19:00.056 --> 00:19:00.974 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA gasps]

00:19:01.057 --> 00:19:04.352 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR]
But her calming ritual!

00:19:04.436 --> 00:19:05.770 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA] This is the
most terrifying thing

00:19:05.854 --> 00:19:07.272 position:50% align:center
I've ever done in my life!

00:19:07.355 --> 00:19:09.733 position:50% align:center
Whoever invented this
game sucks! I hate it!

00:19:09.816 --> 00:19:13.361 position:50% align:center
Save me, Hayasaka!

00:19:15.572 --> 00:19:16.781 position:50% align:center
♪ Let's go, Kaguya,
let's go, yay! ♪

00:19:16.865 --> 00:19:18.241 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
You'll pay.

00:19:18.324 --> 00:19:20.201 position:50% align:center
I swear, even if it's
the last thing I do,

00:19:20.285 --> 00:19:22.704 position:50% align:center
I'll make that
balloon bimbo pay!

00:19:22.787 --> 00:19:25.498 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA grunts]
It's your turn, Ishigami!

00:19:25.582 --> 00:19:28.043 position:50% align:center
You talked so big
yet pumped so little.

00:19:28.126 --> 00:19:30.337 position:50% align:center
Think a scaredy-cat
like you can do better?

00:19:30.420 --> 00:19:33.882 position:50% align:center
[YU] That was the old me.
I'm a whole new man.

00:19:33.965 --> 00:19:36.009 position:50% align:center
Watch.

00:19:36.092 --> 00:19:37.510 position:50% align:center
You'll see.

00:19:37.594 --> 00:19:40.764 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR] Fear is no longer
a factor for young Ishigami.

00:19:40.847 --> 00:19:43.516 position:50% align:center
He broke free from the chains
of anxiety that bound him

00:19:43.600 --> 00:19:45.810 position:50% align:center
and overcame
countless hardships,

00:19:45.894 --> 00:19:48.772 position:50% align:center
all while making new
friends along the way.

00:19:48.855 --> 00:19:50.106 position:50% align:center
[YU]
That's right.

00:19:50.190 --> 00:19:51.733 position:50% align:center
I learned I need to start
keeping my eyes open.

00:19:51.816 --> 00:19:53.735 position:50% align:center
I used to avoid looking
at the things I feared,

00:19:53.818 --> 00:19:55.695 position:50% align:center
but that only made
my fear grow stronger.

00:19:55.779 --> 00:19:57.906 position:50% align:center
If I take a good look--

00:19:57.989 --> 00:20:02.243 position:50% align:center
[YU screams] That dumb thing
scares the hell out of me!

00:20:02.327 --> 00:20:04.662 position:50% align:center
[YU groans]

00:20:04.746 --> 00:20:07.165 position:50% align:center
[YU screams]

00:20:07.248 --> 00:20:08.958 position:50% align:center
I wanna go home!

00:20:09.042 --> 00:20:12.003 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR] The previous episode
was apparently pointless.

00:20:12.087 --> 00:20:13.880 position:50% align:center
Okay, you're next, Fujiwara!

00:20:13.963 --> 00:20:16.758 position:50% align:center
You only had one
pump in you? Coward.

00:20:16.841 --> 00:20:18.259 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
Oh, Fujiwara.

00:20:18.343 --> 00:20:19.844 position:50% align:center
Please have a tangerine.

00:20:19.928 --> 00:20:21.680 position:50% align:center
The rind of citrus fruits
contains limonene,

00:20:21.763 --> 00:20:23.139 position:50% align:center
which can dissolve rubber.

00:20:23.223 --> 00:20:25.725 position:50% align:center
If one drop of juice hits
the balloon, it'll explode!

00:20:25.809 --> 00:20:27.102 position:50% align:center
[CHIKA] I'll have some later.

00:20:27.185 --> 00:20:30.063 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR] That's what
you call a swing and a miss.

00:20:31.147 --> 00:20:32.440 position:50% align:center
Your turn, Miko!

00:20:32.524 --> 00:20:33.692 position:50% align:center
[MIKO gasps]

00:20:33.775 --> 00:20:35.944 position:50% align:center
Who's the one-pump
chump now, ya damn coward?

00:20:36.027 --> 00:20:38.738 position:50% align:center
[whimpers]

00:20:39.781 --> 00:20:42.784 position:50% align:center
Pump, pump, pump it up, Miko!

00:20:42.867 --> 00:20:44.119 position:50% align:center
[CHIKA]
Keep going!

00:20:44.202 --> 00:20:45.495 position:50% align:center
Okay.

00:20:45.578 --> 00:20:46.996 position:50% align:center
[CHIKA]
Quitters never win!

00:20:47.080 --> 00:20:48.039 position:50% align:center
Okay!

00:20:48.123 --> 00:20:49.499 position:50% align:center
--[CHIKA] Just pump!
--[MIKO] Okay!

00:20:49.582 --> 00:20:52.544 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR] In that moment
they knew Fujiwara was scum.

00:20:52.627 --> 00:20:54.212 position:50% align:center
[whimpers]

00:20:54.295 --> 00:20:56.840 position:50% align:center
Prove you've got what
it takes to be president!

00:20:56.923 --> 00:20:59.426 position:50% align:center
The greater the fear,
the more valuable your courage!

00:20:59.509 --> 00:21:01.636 position:50% align:center
You're an inspiration to us all!

00:21:01.720 --> 00:21:04.014 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR]
Yeah, they're scum, too.

00:21:04.097 --> 00:21:06.391 position:50% align:center
[GROUP cheering]

00:21:06.474 --> 00:21:08.476 position:50% align:center
Is this satisfactory, guys?

00:21:08.560 --> 00:21:10.061 position:50% align:center
I don't think it
can stand any more.

00:21:10.145 --> 00:21:11.187 position:50% align:center
[GROUP cheering]

00:21:11.271 --> 00:21:12.731 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:21:15.567 --> 00:21:17.027 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI gasps]

00:21:17.110 --> 00:21:19.529 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA] So long as it doesn't
pop on my turn, I'm victorious!

00:21:19.612 --> 00:21:21.406 position:50% align:center
I'm only doing this
because I want to win!

00:21:21.489 --> 00:21:22.866 position:50% align:center
It has nothing to do
with me being afraid!

00:21:22.949 --> 00:21:24.868 position:50% align:center
--[MIYUKI grrunts]
--[KAGUYA inhales]

00:21:25.910 --> 00:21:26.661 position:50% align:center
[MIKO gasps]

00:21:26.745 --> 00:21:28.455 position:50% align:center
Was that a... bug?

00:21:28.538 --> 00:21:30.665 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA] Yes! It was
flying around your head!

00:21:30.749 --> 00:21:32.584 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR]
Game over, man!

00:21:32.667 --> 00:21:35.503 position:50% align:center
Not even Kaguya can mask
the despair she feels!

00:21:35.587 --> 00:21:37.380 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
Shinomiya.

00:21:37.464 --> 00:21:40.342 position:50% align:center
This must be harder for
you than the rest of us.

00:21:40.425 --> 00:21:41.676 position:50% align:center
I bet you're only
playing because

00:21:41.760 --> 00:21:44.054 position:50% align:center
you didn't want to
ruin it for everyone else.

00:21:44.137 --> 00:21:45.930 position:50% align:center
If that's the case...

00:21:46.931 --> 00:21:48.808 position:50% align:center
[PAPA SHIROGANE]
Miyuki.

00:21:48.892 --> 00:21:52.437 position:50% align:center
I'm not what you'd
classify as a "good person."

00:21:52.520 --> 00:21:56.024 position:50% align:center
There isn't anything I can teach
you you can't learn from a book.

00:21:56.107 --> 00:21:59.694 position:50% align:center
But... I want you to
make me a promise, okay?

00:21:59.778 --> 00:22:02.030 position:50% align:center
Promise you'll always
protect your friends

00:22:02.113 --> 00:22:03.531 position:50% align:center
and the woman you love,

00:22:03.615 --> 00:22:06.868 position:50% align:center
because that's what
a good man's supposed to do.

00:22:06.951 --> 00:22:10.538 position:50% align:center
He doesn't back down.
He faces problems head-on.

00:22:10.622 --> 00:22:13.083 position:50% align:center
Become that kind of man.

00:22:14.542 --> 00:22:17.962 position:50% align:center
That's the one thing
I ask of you, father to son.

00:22:18.046 --> 00:22:19.589 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
Dad...

00:22:19.673 --> 00:22:22.550 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR] The son recalled
his father's touching words...

00:22:22.634 --> 00:22:24.386 position:50% align:center
Hey! Looks like
it's your turn again!

00:22:24.469 --> 00:22:26.471 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR]
...and completely ignored them!

00:22:26.554 --> 00:22:29.933 position:50% align:center
Well, good luck to ya!

00:22:30.016 --> 00:22:32.435 position:50% align:center
Thanks for the tangerine!

00:22:32.519 --> 00:22:33.770 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR]
Just in case you missed it,

00:22:33.853 --> 00:22:35.980 position:50% align:center
those citrus rinds
contain limonene,

00:22:36.064 --> 00:22:37.357 position:50% align:center
which can dissolve rubber.

00:22:37.440 --> 00:22:40.110 position:50% align:center
So if one drop of juice
were to hit that balloon...

00:22:40.193 --> 00:22:41.736 position:50% align:center
Yep!

00:22:42.404 --> 00:22:44.614 position:50% align:center
Good-bye, cruel world.

00:22:44.698 --> 00:22:48.243 position:50% align:center
[yells] But I haven't
accomplished anything yet!

00:22:48.326 --> 00:22:51.121 position:50% align:center
[CHIKA]
Sky burial!

00:22:52.163 --> 00:22:55.000 position:50% align:center
[alarm blares]

00:22:56.084 --> 00:22:57.627 position:50% align:center
[ADOLPHE laughs]

00:22:57.711 --> 00:23:00.296 position:50% align:center
[NAGISA giggles]

00:23:00.380 --> 00:23:04.718 position:50% align:center
[screams]

00:23:04.801 --> 00:23:06.594 position:50% align:center
[OSARAGI]
I'm watching you.

00:23:10.557 --> 00:23:14.728 position:50% align:center
[BOTH]
Are you ready? Blast off!

00:23:14.811 --> 00:23:19.065 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR] Results for
today's battle are... invalid.

00:23:19.149 --> 00:23:21.067 position:50% align:center
Even so...

00:23:22.861 --> 00:23:25.572 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI sighs]
Think, Miyuki.

00:23:25.655 --> 00:23:27.907 position:50% align:center
Don't lend her a hand
like it's nothing.

00:23:27.991 --> 00:23:30.702 position:50% align:center
Stay calm, cool, and collected

00:23:30.785 --> 00:23:32.996 position:50% align:center
as you draw out her
affection for you!

00:23:33.079 --> 00:23:34.998 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
Now's your chance, Kaguya.

00:23:35.081 --> 00:23:37.417 position:50% align:center
Put your girlish
wiles to good use!

00:23:37.500 --> 00:23:40.337 position:50% align:center
The very second he takes your
hand, he'll be putty in it!

00:23:40.420 --> 00:23:43.340 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
Shinomiya, you okay?

00:23:43.423 --> 00:23:45.216 position:50% align:center
Yes.

00:23:47.302 --> 00:23:49.471 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
And if all goes well...

00:23:52.974 --> 00:23:55.685 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA] ...he'll confess
his love for me!

00:23:57.228 --> 00:23:59.647 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR]
The battle rages on.

00:23:59.731 --> 00:24:01.149 position:50% align:center
And on.

00:24:01.232 --> 00:24:05.320 position:50% align:center
And on, and on, on, on, onward!

00:24:05.403 --> 00:24:09.074 position:50% align:center
On and--yeah, you get the idea.